Class CompiledJavaCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centurylink.mdw.java.CompiledJavaCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CacheEnabled, ExcludableCache, PreloadableCache, RegisteredService, CacheService

    public class CompiledJavaCache
extends Object
implements PreloadableCache, ExcludableCache
    Compiles and caches java asset classes, and provides a class-loading mechanism to allow these assets to reference Jar classes as well.
